00f3n de S. Antonio, en las partes\u00a0de Etiop\u00eda y Egypto<\/em>. Gerona: Antonio Oliva,. 260\u00a0p. We do not know who the author of <em>Vida y milagros&#8230;<\/em> is; however, it is very possible that the added text\u00a0\u2013 <em>Grandezas de la religi\u00f3n&#8230;<\/em> \u2013 is a reproduction of a famous book of its time, prior to this edition by Navarro, and whose author\u00a0is a person\u00a0abundantly\u00a0cited by Aponte and represented in the Book of Paintings (not only the author but also the book in question):<\/p>\n<p class=\"body-text\">Baltazar Abissino, Juan de, 1609.-\u00a0<em>Fundacion, vida y regla de la grande orden militar\u00a0y monastica de los caualleros y monges del glorioso Padre San Anton Abad, en la Etiopia, monarchia\u00a0del Preste Iuan de las Indias compuesta por don\u00a0Iuan de Baltazar Abissino<\/em>.- Valencia: Juan\u00a0Vicente Franco, 1609 [4], 24 h. ; 4\u00ba. This book was authored by an Egyptian monk of the Order and translated and published later in French:\u00a0Abyffin, Dom Iean Baltazar 1632 &#8211; <em>La Fondation,\u00a0Vie, et Reigle, dv Grand Ordre Militaire, &amp;\u00a0Monaftique, des Cheualiers Religieux, du glorieux\u00a0Pere S. Antoine en Ethiopie, Monarchie du\u00a0Prete-Iean, des Indes. Compos\u00e9 en Efpagnol, par\u00a0un Cheualier Abyffin, Religieux &amp; Militaire du\u00a0mefme Ordre<\/em>. -. Et mis en Francois par vn Religieux\u00a0de la Congregation reform\u00e9e de l\u2019Ordre\u00a0de S. Antoine de Viennois F.M.L.F, Paris: Iean\u00a0Tompere. 30 + 116 pp. (<a href=\"http:\/\/aponte.hosting.nyu.edu\/bibliography\/\">Pavez Ojeda 2006a, 757-758<\/a>)<\/p>\n<p class=\"body-text\">Google Books provides access to <a href=\"https:\/\/books.google.com\/books?id=lFaotJrhEVcC&amp;pg=PR1#v=onepage&amp;q&amp;f=false\">Navarro&#8217;s 1683 edition<\/a>\u00a0(published in Barcelona)\u00a0as well Pavez&#8217;s second suggestion,\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/books.google.com\/books?id=jOAWe_Z77B4C&amp;dq=Fundacion%2C%20vida%20y%20regla%20de%20la%20grande%20orden%20militar%20y%20monastica&amp;pg=PP1#v=onepage&amp;q=Fundacion,%20vida%20y%20regla%20de%20la%20grande%20orden%20militar%20y%20monastica&amp;f=false\">Baltazar Abissino&#8217;s\u00a0<\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/books.google.com\/books?id=jOAWe_Z77B4C&amp;dq=Fundacion%2C%20vida%20y%20regla%20de%20la%20grande%20orden%20militar%20y%20monastica&amp;pg=PP1#v=onepage&amp;q=Fundacion,%20vida%20y%20regla%20de%20la%20grande%20orden%20militar%20y%20monastica&amp;f=false\">1609\u00a0<\/a><em><a href=\"https:\/\/books.google.com\/books?id=jOAWe_Z77B4C&amp;dq=Fundacion%2C%20vida%20y%20regla%20de%20la%20grande%20orden%20militar%20y%20monastica&amp;pg=PP1#v=onepage&amp;q=Fundacion,%20vida%20y%20regla%20de%20la%20grande%20orden%20militar%20y%20monastica&amp;f=false\">Fundacion, vida y regla de la grande orden militar\u00a0y monastica de los caualleros y monges del glorioso Padre San Anton Abad<\/a>.<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Identified in the trial record as: El libro de la vida de San Antonio Abad Commentary by Pavez Ojeda: &#8220;Stephan Palmi\u00e9 identifies this book as:\u00a01683 &#8211; Vida y milagros del pr\u00edncipe de los\u00a0anacoretas, padre de los Cenobiarcas Nuestro Padre\u00a0S. Antonio [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"page-templates\/full-width.php","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/aponte.hosting.nyu.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/923"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/aponte.hosting.nyu.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/aponte.hosting.nyu.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/aponte.hosting.nyu.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/aponte.hosting.nyu.edu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=923"}],"version-history":[{"count":15,"href":"http:\/\/apont